txt.en: Maddened marsh-crows can be found in the marshes, east of Oserley.\n\nYou should drive off the draug-maddened marsh-crows from the marshes.
Maddened marsh-crows from the Wódfen have crossed the Entwash into the marshes east of Oserley, attacking everything they see.
